<p>You cannot improve what you do not measure. Brand SEO requires different metrics than traditional keyword tracking.</p>
<h3>Track Branded Search Volume</h3>
<p>Use Google Search Console to monitor impressions and clicks for queries containing your brand name. Track this monthly and look for trends.</p>
